ReferenceDocuments.name: HTAN-Instruction
ReferenceDocuments.description: Participant identifier ::= _integer where HTAN_Center_ID is the identifier assigned to the atlas. For example, if you are part of the CHOP research center, and you have three research participants, you will need to create three HTAN Identifiers.  For example:  HTA4_1 HTA4_2 HTA4_3
